commit.message:
i386.h (TARGET_CPU_CPP_BUILTINS): Reformat.

2007-04-05  H.J. Lu  <hongjiu.lu@intel.com>

	* config/i386/i386.h (TARGET_CPU_CPP_BUILTINS): Reformat.
